{"tid":1082614,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯遭前度轟耽於性事：你很軟！","createTime":"2019-03-29T05:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:51:40.000Z","uid":1426,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"897e77d366509e89a5fcb3096c3896a1c46acb58","tid":1082614,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=bc60cb1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙模特兒和女主持人Alba Carrillo不滿皇家馬德里門將泰拔高圖爾斯在節目中談及愛情，炮轟對方是耽於性事。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里門將泰拔高圖爾斯（Thibaut Courtois）捅中蜜蜂窩，他在接受馬德里電台訪問時，談到前模特兒女友Alba Carrillo，表示自己已經移情別戀，「我們月初已經分手，我們不再是情侶。」Alba Carrilo對此十分不滿，在回應時大爆高圖爾斯的私隱。<br />\n<br />\n「我過去夠保護這位先生！如果你有兩個小孩的話，最好還是管好你的老二，因那不是我要做的事。」Alba Carrillo暗示高圖爾斯有外遇，甚至暗示他耽於性事：「你那東西非常軟！」<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯一向風流成性，未成名前就搶走奇雲迪布尼的女友，後來在馬德里體育會認識前女友杜明姬絲，對方替他生下兩個孩子，但仍然被他始亂終棄，投入Alba Carrillo的懷抱。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 電視畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjdquQx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjdquQx.png&h=dd42cb1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"476a973d2d0ab2975a312478b47581011e7ec536","tid":1082614,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"259性無能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ff8ad538293a491c14ae6f656e26f61843c459","tid":1082614,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"死得其所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0534bb1f2f57850a1cfb9963fde7d9bda9e6e0","tid":1082614,"uid":35507,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"呢條反骨仔真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b788c892dd9d5aba8bf00eaac300fc5e542240","tid":1082614,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"